{"tid":855164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵再減福田班次止蝕","createTime":"2018-10-10T01:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T16:09:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":117,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff0554b2c63aaac82df714a315cd1ba450ffaa1","tid":855164,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181010/20518739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F20518739&d=pVqiA2KGJfIis%2Bm8MYXWdTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5157224a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F20518739&h=f30090cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181010/20518739</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月10日 <br />\n<br />\n高鐵再減福田班次止蝕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181010/large/10la6p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181010%2Flarge%2F10la6p10.jpg&h=16ba82d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高鐵香港段本月26日起取消24班來往深圳福田的周末特別班次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】廣深港高鐵香港段乘客量持續未能達標，港鐵決定減班止蝕，由本月26日起取消24班來往深圳福田的周末特別班次。今次已是高鐵香港段通車兩星期多以來第二次減班，十&bull;一長假高𥧌期原定每天開出127對列車，但因乘客量未如預期，需大幅減至每日83對。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周末特別班次取消<br />\n<br />\n根據港鐵公佈資料，高鐵香港段來往西九站至福田，周一至周四每日開出15對共30班車，周五至周日則開出27對共54班車，即每日早上7時半至晚上10半加開12對共24班周末特別班次。但由本月26日起，所有周末特別班次都取消。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人表示，內地鐵總會按最新營運情況及乘客需求，在有需要時調整實際開出班次。高鐵香港段將維持每天至少83對長短途班次。高鐵香港至福田車程14分鐘，但連同提早45分鐘到西九站一地兩檢，即需時一小時。<br />\n<br />\n車費由最低的二等座78元至商務座234元。有網民指出，現時搭西鐵到元朗轉乘九巴B1，或搭直通巴士到深圳，車費僅30多元。高鐵車費太貴節省時間不多， 無競爭力。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n宏光護老院10外勞　僅追回近半欠薪<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n冷氣技工疑觸電亡　妻頭撼閘討殮葬費"},{"pid":"a9e1b97e7b413c1375458571b71b222ed78eb807","tid":855164,"uid":158613,"like":187,"dislike":1,"score":186,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:44:02.000Z","msg":"取消所有班次 係蝕最少嘅方法"},{"pid":"bb348d9bc276385828772df31dd34ae00b2c733d","tid":855164,"uid":42820,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:45:30.000Z","msg":"事到如今cut晒啲車應該係止蝕嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2478ddd43fa3064d82cd64ee7552e7e6230ff447","tid":855164,"uid":21545,"like":38,"dislike":5,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"對車 單車啲fd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d01886f225d636e48983b0c6ad47777972cbb8","tid":855164,"uid":116330,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"一早都諗到邊個會比$78去深圳<br />\n商務客? 公司會叫你坐相對較平又快捷既交通工具<br />\n一係有自己車<br />\n<br />\n係班狗官諗唔到<br />\n而家每日幾萬個西九客有幾多個商務客?"},{"pid":"a5276f523b3fa27cf2bde465379fd3ea5ca29d42","tid":855164,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:53:18.000Z","msg":"廢鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07dd48edf72d96356bc548a57b77d98dc6b60819","tid":855164,"uid":56900,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"09d01886f225d636e48983b0c6ad47777972cbb8","tid":855164,"uid":116330,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"一早都諗到邊個會比$78去深圳<br />\n商務客? 公司會叫你坐相對較平又快捷既交通工具<br />\n一係有自己車<br />\n<br />\n係班狗官諗唔到<br />\n而家每日幾萬個西九客有幾多個商務客?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:53:47.000Z","msg":"班狗官點會諗唔到"},{"pid":"a684e4271039f3e39407f4154ad20cbe0c0aec52","tid":855164,"uid":160662,"like":4,"dislike":91,"score":-87,"quote":{"pid":"07dd48edf72d96356bc548a57b77d98dc6b60819","tid":855164,"uid":56900,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":